{"tid":601064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有/曾經有拖延症，入嚟分享下你病情","createTime":"2018-03-22T02:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T21:07:31.000Z","uid":173349,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a71a1a7a074d5870a34666250b299ec03b2e60f6","tid":601064,"uid":173349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:00:43.000Z","msg":"有嘅講下你地病重到咩地步，<br />\n曾經有嘅分享下點樣走出嚟，放下暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚憎自己呢個習性，屌你老母今年24歲唔撚想再有呢個病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每日起床都拖，有野做就拖到遲到，無野做就拖到肚餓都唔起身再訓著多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n交咩費都拖，拖到過deadline比人罰錢先嚟後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明當日無野做可以處理啲事務都要拖，明日復明日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由讀書做deadline fighter到以家做野跑數，永遠都拖到最後一刻先嚟做，到最後做唔切就索性唔做，之後又後悔先on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：無家底，屋企第時等我養，好撚想改"},{"pid":"2d5b7f2a13071e4c2fc6448e180da5f5da82b100","tid":601064,"uid":142532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:01:31.000Z","msg":"聽日要交FYP 未掂過"},{"pid":"552e5b26806e93f7b49c44698af960448e1124b1","tid":601064,"uid":125733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:02:25.000Z","msg":"this is the sign of cleverness"},{"pid":"5ec6664f7305ecd6c01993863e9e4ddec3fcc952","tid":601064,"uid":173349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d5b7f2a13071e4c2fc6448e180da5f5da82b100","tid":601064,"uid":142532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:01:31.000Z","msg":"聽日要交FYP 未掂過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:03:37.000Z","msg":"讀書時期same"},{"pid":"4695b79619015f54eec168f256bc6bc1badb0fa4","tid":601064,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:07:45.000Z","msg":"冇人Push就乜都唔想做<br />\n返工有啲嘢明明要喺上年年尾做完<br />\n但我拖到依家都未做完<br />\n近一年身體有啲毛病<br />\n但懶去睇醫生<br />\n幾年冇洗牙<br />\n但懶去book<br />\n講咗十幾年去學日文<br />\n啱啱先開始上堂<br />\n<br />\n不過如果有deadline我點拖都唔會遲過deadline<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dada926ea8a4600f944118e23ba30ae455392fd1","tid":601064,"uid":1177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:08:19.000Z","msg":"7點放工想沖涼, 無野做都可以拖到11點先沖,<br />\n起身想落街買早餐可以拖到下午茶就黎餓死先去買"},{"pid":"817f17b93915f48868bcf8b28e14b34acb3e7a85","tid":601064,"uid":175645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:21:16.000Z","msg":"中學返20日欠交足20日，返u次次做deadline fighter. 俾d白痴手機game迷住，過兩日要test都未温"},{"pid":"7cb55b6e40c76bd387be844aa6dcea458dbddb8b","tid":601064,"uid":173349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T05:32:07.000Z","msg":"有無戒甩左嘅巴打分享下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841563673d50988e47985a231b31d3ee60005f21","tid":601064,"uid":173349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"552e5b26806e93f7b49c44698af960448e1124b1","tid":601064,"uid":125733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:02:25.000Z","msg":"this is the sign of cleverness"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T05:32:44.000Z","msg":"講真呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01765ebe18e73fb523c1806099e7ccb38afde040","tid":601064,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"除左拖延症<br />\n仲有好嚴重既唔敢病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97391b31aca381bd86cdf731fc7b62413b130db1","tid":601064,"uid":175950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T05:33:58.000Z","msg":"返工唔到最後一刻都唔會出打門，係其實係屋企冇咩野做"},{"pid":"ab3b4f3d5918c998658d9dbeae0eb3dbdcad0913","tid":601064,"uid":173349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01765ebe18e73fb523c180